#        Python crawler / PostgreSQL + Redis / Cursor AI + Claude Code
# =============================================================================


# =============================================================================
# 0. SECRETS — never commit (Claude API key, DB password, etc.)
# =============================================================================
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.sample
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
secrets/
credentials.json
service-account*.json
application-local.yml
application-local.yaml
application-local.properties


